  "title": "Automotive Mechanic",
  "description": "<p><br>\nOur client is a global leader in gateway services, who is seeking to recruit an Automotive Mechanic. This position is based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Automotive Mechanic</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Plan, schedule and achieve workshop maintenance production for equipment and/or vehicles</p>\n<p>· Manage in-house workforce, and/or outsourced contractor production/shift supervisors, and shift planning</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Comfortable with shift work</p>\n<p>• Nitec/ Higher Nitec in Engineering</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JJ Consulting Services</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg stating position applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br>\n<br>\nWe thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
